      <title>獨家：文件顯示，花旗集團預計貸款簿將在氣候行動升級中受到打擊</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/sustainable-finance-reporting/citigroup-sees-loan-book-hit-climate-action-ramp-up-document-shows-2024-05-01/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根據路透社審閱的美國銀行所準備的機密分析，如果世界加快應對氣候變遷的努力，花旗集團的貸款帳簿可能會遭受數十億美元的損失。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/sustainable-finance-reporting/citigroup-sees-loan-book-hit-climate-action-ramp-up-document-shows-2024-05-01/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 10:03:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
