      <pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 05:13:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>華爾街動盪之際，投資人在全球尋找庇護所</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-europe-analysis-pix-2024-05-01/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[全球投資者正在關注歐洲和新興市場資產，以保護自己免受美國股票和債券進一步動盪的影響，因為頑固的通膨導致對聯準會降息時機的押注被修改。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-europe-analysis-pix-2024-05-01/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 05:07:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由於通貨膨脹削弱了政策寬鬆的希望，聯準會將維持利率穩定</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/fed-hold-rates-steady-inflation-dims-hopes-policy-easing-2024-05-01/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美國央行官員將於週三結束最新的為期兩天的政策會議，聯準會主席鮑威爾將發表新的聲明和評論，這可能會讓人們更清楚地了解最近令人失望的通膨數據如何改變了今年降息的預期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/fed-hold-rates-steady-inflation-dims-hopes-policy-easing-2024-05-01/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 05:03:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美國倫敦房地產支出反彈至八年來最高水平</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us-spending-london-real-estate-rebounds-highest-eight-years-2024-05-01/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法國巴黎銀行房地產部門編制的數據顯示，美國投資者正以八年來最快的速度購買倫敦商業房地產，因為有跡象顯示英國市場的復甦速度快於遭受重創的美國。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us-spending-london-real-estate-rebounds-highest-eight-years-2024-05-01/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 05:02:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>馬斯克解散特斯拉電動車充電團隊，讓客戶蒙在鼓裡</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/musk-disbands-tesla-ev-charging-team-leaving-customers-dark-2024-04-30/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[產業官員和分析師週二表示，馬斯克突然決定解僱負責特斯拉電動車充電業務的員工，這讓那些準備為客戶配備新電動車以使用特斯拉超級充電網路的汽車製造商措手不及。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/musk-disbands-tesla-ev-charging-team-leaving-customers-dark-2024-04-30/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 20:23:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
